{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Call referendum on introducing death penalty for certain offences",
        "additional_details": "We believe that the technological advances and DNA testing facilities mean that judgements in relation to such crimes are likely to be accurate.",
        "background": "We call on the Government to conduct a referendum of whether to introduce the death penalty by hanging for offences of: treason, murder, rape and terrorism.",
